02:11.330 --> 02:12.683
THAT MAYBE
WE SHOULD GET TOGETHER.

02:12.730 --> 02:15.028
WHY ON EARTH WOULD YOU THINK
THAT'S A GOOD IDEA?

02:15.070 --> 02:16.162
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

