02:36.610 --> 02:39.340
YES, I BELIEVE I AM.

02:39.380 --> 02:40.711
SEVEN, IT IS.

02:40.750 --> 02:43.981
I'LL BE THE ONE FLARING
MY NOSTRILS UNCONTROLLABLY.

02:44.020 --> 02:46.329
[laughs]

02:59.090 --> 03:00.352
