JUST DO THAT TO PROVE A POINT.

03:08.840 --> 03:10.137
SHE'S A REAL PERSON, SHAWN.
THAT'S NO JOKE.

03:10.180 --> 03:11.602
[phone ringing]

03:11.650 --> 03:13.470
