03:18.590 --> 03:20.524
THAT WAS WEIRD.

03:20.560 --> 03:22.869
(Vick)
WE RECEIVED THE FOLLOWING
LE'I'I'ER ABOUT AN HOUR AGO.

03:22.900 --> 03:23.889
IT HAS BEEN AUTHENTICATED.

03:23.940 --> 03:25.703
IT'S FROM THE YIN YANG KILLER.

03:25.740 --> 03:27.776
PAY CLOSE ATTENTION.

03:27.810 --> 03:29.516
(Lassiter)
"HEY EVERYBODY, I'M BACK.

03:29.550 --> 03:30.847
"FOR ONE NIGHT ONLY.

03:30.880 --> 03:32.689
"I'M GOING TO KILL SOMEONE
TONIGHT.

03:32.720 --> 03:35.086
"GUESS WHO, GUESS WHERE,
GUESS HOW.

03:35.130 --> 03:36.449
THIS IS GOING
TO BE SO MUCH FUN."

03:36.500 --> 03:38.718
SIGNED, "MR. YANG."

03:38.770 --> 03:40.169
HE'S LOOKING
FOR A NEW CHALLENGER.

03:40.200 --> 03:40.996
THAT'S WHAT HE DOES.

03:41.040 --> 03:42.803
CHIEF, I BELIEVE
HE'S SPEAKING TO ME.

03:42.840 --> 03:44.501
TRUST ME.
I AM READY.

03:51.590 --> 03:53.080
[snorts]
OH, COME ON, PEOPLE.

03:53.130 --> 03:55.064
HE COULD BE TALKING
ABOUT ANYBODY.

03:55.100 --> 03:56.089
JUST LAST WEEK,

03:56.130 --> 03:58.234
