* I KNOW YOU KNOW

04:17.880 --> 04:20.178
* THEY JUST DON'T HAVE
ANY PROOF *

04:20.210 --> 04:21.541
* EMBRACE THE DECEPTION

04:21.590 --> 04:22.841
* LEARN HOW TO BEND

